accessibility.text: Session::set(key, value) - Add a key/value pair to the session
Session::has(key) - Determines if key has a value
Session::get(key) - Returns the value for key
Session::forget(key) - Removes key from the session
Session::pull(key, value) - Returns the value for key and forgets key
Session::push(key, value) - Assumes key is an array and pushes value to the end of that array
Session::all() - Get all data in the session
Session::flush() - Removes all data from the session
